title: Morgan Wallen In Studio + Milk And Cereal Debate + Top 10 Most Hated Country Songs
itunes:title: Morgan Wallen In Studio + Milk And Cereal Debate + Top 10 Most Hated Country Songs
description:
Morgan Wallen stops by the studio to talk about his new album, how Wal-Mart leaked it and he performs with his band. Bobby reads a poll he saw on the B-TEAM Facebook page about what you do with the milk after eating cereal. Plus, we all debate a list of what are considered to be the worst country songs of all-time!
